lead_paragraph: Ai Miyazato of Japan, celebrating her 23rd birthday, shot a four-under 68 to join Cristie Kerr and five South Korean players atop the crowded leader board at the Wegmans L.P.G.A. in Rochester. Jeong Jang, Inbee Park, Song-Hee Kim, Jimin Jeong and Soo-Yun Kang, who holed a 9-wood shot for an ace on the 165-yard seventh hole, also shot 68s.
